reviewText: The music producers did a very good job of remixing the older performances to make them sound up to date.

If you're looking for a primer on what drum corps was in the 70s, 80s, 90s, and now, this is a great collection to track the evolution of the activity. Sound and video-quality wise, it's pretty close to the DVDs, but this particular collection is only available on Blu-Ray.
